out_data: Disaster projects related to construction that have been completed in the past include Citywide Guardrail Replacement and Malibu Park Storm Drain Repairs. Projects funded by FEMA and CalOES include Guardrail Replacement Citywide, Corral Canyon Road Bridge Repairs, Birdview Avenue Improvements, and Clover Heights Storm Drain.
